 keywords = {CMOS integrated circuits; Failure (mechanical); Magnetic recording; MRAM devices; Block error correction pointer; Block errors; Error correction coding; Errors correction; Hard errors; Magnetic random access memory; Spin transfer torque; Spin-transfer torque magnetic random access memory; Sub-blocks; Error correction},
