 keywords = {Benchmarking; Particle beams; Photonic devices; Photons; Quantum electronics; Quantum entanglement; Quantum optics; Computing paradigm; Entangled photons; Fidelity; Measurement-based; Measurement-based quantum computing; Photon qubits; Quantum Computing; Quantum computing circuits; Sub-circuits; Wire cutting; Qubits},
